def fib():
	a,b = 1,2
	yield a
	yield b
	while True:
		a,b = b,a+b
		yield b
def subfib(start,end):
	for num in fib():
		if num > end: return
		if num >= start:
			yield num

	start,end = [int(x) for x in raw_input().split(" ")]
